reviews.text: Came here for second time. Good place to have yummy dim sum at cheap price and no service charge. Generous amount and really good food quality though the environment may not be up to standard but still acceptable for me. Will come again when I am round.
A food variety of dim sum. Freshly made. Very good price

Great place, I enjoyed it a lot. Food took a little bit longer (than other places) to be prepared but it's because most of it is freshly made in the kitchen. The portions are big and is cheaper compared to many other places. Definitely going back.
Roasted goose was juicy and succulent. Obviously a hot spot for locals. Don’t expect English menu. Pictures do just fine. But it’s for the goose tour going.
A treasure trove of brilliantly made local dim sum. They serve dim sum till 10pm. They also have clay pot rice.

reviews.text: Came here for second time. Good place to have yummy dim sum at cheap price and no service charge. Generous amount and really good food quality though the environment may not be up to standard but still acceptable for me. Will come again when I am round.
傳統味道中式點心，款式多，即叫即蒸，價錢相宜，抵食夾大件，伙計與客人互動態度頗佳。唯一扣分是裝修太殘舊，表面不太吸引非街坊的外來客。
食物質素不錯，即叫即蒸，要等十多至二十分鐘
我無討厭此地方，食物唔差，價錢大衆化.
A food variety of dim sum. Freshly made. Very good price
